data.description: FANTASTIC LOCATION: a quick hop to the HWY, around the corner from shopping, schools & parks, and adjacent to the Ridgecrest & Centennial golf courses! In the gated Greens at Ridgecrest, you have all the benefits of being close to everything without the overwhelming sense that the hustle & bustle is at your door. Come enjoy low-maintenance living, private streets & sidewalks, manicured common areas, and clubhouse access for community get-togethers and hosting family & friends. Got a boat/RV? We’ve got a secure parking area for that, too! This beautiful craftsman-style home, tucked away on a quiet cul-de-sac, features a south-facing front porch, an open floor plan with a spacious great room and vaulted ceilings, a generous-sized dining area, and a kitchen with pantry and an island with a breakfast bar. The generous-sized master suite offers a dual vanity and walk-in closet. Recently repainted interior and high-efficiency furnace installed in 2021. Community permits fencing of back & side yard areas.
